name: Change the password by receiving an email link

steps.name: Check element is visible and clickable: ('xpath', '//section//a')
Check element is visible and clickable: ('xpath', '//*[@type="submit"]')
Wait until url: https://brainup.site/profile will be changed.
Check element is visible and clickable: ('xpath', '//a[@href="/profile"]')
Check element is visible and clickable: ('xpath', '//a[@href="/password-recovery"]')
Clear field the email and enter data
Check element is visible and clickable: ('css selector', 'form [type="button"]')
Get a link to change the password by email
Enter the data in the email field
Check element is visible and clickable: ('xpath', '//button[@type="submit"]')
Check element is visible and clickable: ('xpath', '//section//a')
The user has authorised with new password
Check element is visible and clickable: ('xpath', '//*[@type="submit"]')

Clear field the email and enter data
Check element is visible and clickable: ('css selector', 'form [type="button"]')
Get a link to change the password by email
Enter old password in the email field
